(3, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 1, 'About us', 'about-us', 'About us', 'About us', 'About us', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">About us:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Patna\r\nMetro Rail Corporation Limited (<b>PMRCL</b>) aims to transform the urban\r\ntransportation landscape in the historic city of Patna. With a vision to create\r\na sustainable, efficient and convenient Mass Rapid Transit System, PMRCL is\r\ndedicated to providing world-class metro services that meet the needs of our\r\ncitizens and improve the overall quality of life in the region.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Our Mission:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Our\r\nprimary & foremost goal is to build a state-of-the-art metro network in\r\nPatna that provides seamless connectivity, reduces traffic congestion, and\r\npromotes environment friendly commuting options. We aim to provide safe,\r\nreliable and affordable transport solutions to the city\'s residents, daily commuters\r\nand visitors.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Key Goals:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Urban Development:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> PMRCL aims to contribute in the rapid urban\r\ndevelopment of Patna by providing an efficient & economical public\r\ntransportation system that promotes smart growth and reduces the city\'s carbon\r\nfootprint.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Customer-centric approach:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> we prioritize the need and comfort of our passengers\r\nand ensure that every ride in the Patna Metro having a pleasant and picturesque\r\nexperience. From state of the art, air-conditioned metro cars to aristocratic stations,\r\nour focus is to meet the expectations of our valued passengers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Sustainability and Environmental\r\nResponsibility:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> As part of\r\nour commitment to sustainability, we actively implement environment friendly\r\npractices in our operations. By encouraging the use of public transit, we seek\r\nto reduce the city\'s dependence on private transportation, thereby mitigating\r\nour environmental impact.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Safety and Security:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> Safety is our top priority. We adhere to strict\r\nsafety measures and use the state-of-the-art technology to ensure the\r\nwell-being of our passengers. Our competent & skilled staff works tirelessly\r\nto create a safe environment throughout our metro network.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Employment and Skills\r\nDevelopment:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> PMRCL prides itself\r\non its role as a begetter of employment opportunities. By promoting skill\r\ndevelopment, we help to improve the employability of local populace.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Technological Advancement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> We rely on technological innovations to improve\r\nthe efficiency and effectiveness of our metro services. From advanced signaling\r\nsystems to user-friendly applications, we are committed to leveraging the\r\nlatest advancements for the benefit of our valued passengers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Transparency and Accountability:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> PMRCL operates with the utmost transparency and\r\naccountability. We value the trust that our stakeholders place in us and ensure\r\nthat our decision-making processes are open, fair and in line with the best\r\npractices in corporate governance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Together\r\nwith the support of the Government, our dedicated team, and the people of\r\nPatna, we are committed to building a world-class metro network that will not\r\nonly serve the city\'s growing population, but also act as a catalyst for\r\neconomic development and social progress.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Thank\r\nyou for choosing <b>Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited</b> as your preferred\r\nmode of transportation. Let us embark together on a journey to a greener,\r\nbetter connected and prosperous Patna.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">If\r\nyou have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us. We are\r\nhere to serve you better.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\">The\r\nTeam of Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n\"Century Gothic\",sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 2, 0, 'Ønbsp\r\nAbout us', '2023-09-20 04:12:33', '2024-12-04 05:49:29'),
(4, NULL, 1, 3, 1, 1, 'About PMRCL', 'about-pmrcl', 'About PMRCL', 'About PMRCL', 'About PMRCL', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\">Patna Metro\r\nRail Corporation Limited (</span><b style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\">PMRCL</b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\">) aims to transform the urban\r\ntransportation landscape in the historic city of Patna. With a vision to create\r\na sustainable, efficient and convenient Mass Rapid Transit System, PMRCL is\r\ndedicated to providing world-class metro services that meet the needs of our\r\ncitizens and improve the overall quality of life in the region.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\"><b>Our Mission:</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;=\"\" mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Our primary\r\n&amp; foremost goal is to build a state-of-the-art metro network in Patna that\r\nprovides seamless connectivity, reduces traffic congestion, and promotes\r\nenvironment friendly commuting options. We aim to provide safe, reliable and\r\naffordable transport solutions to the city\'s residents, daily commuters and\r\nvisitors.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Key Goals:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Urban Development:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;PMRCL aims to contribute in the rapid urban development of\r\nPatna by providing an efficient &amp; economical public transportation system\r\nthat promotes smart growth and reduces the city\'s carbon footprint.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Customer-centric approach:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;we prioritize the need and comfort of our passengers and\r\nensure that every ride in the Patna Metro having a pleasant and picturesque\r\nexperience. From state of the art, air-conditioned metro cars to aristocratic\r\nstations, our focus is to meet the expectations of our valued passengers.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Sustainability and Environmental\r\nResponsibility:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;As part of our commitment to\r\nsustainability, we actively implement environment friendly practices in our\r\noperations. By encouraging the use of public transit, we seek to reduce the\r\ncity\'s dependence on private transportation, thereby mitigating our\r\nenvironmental impact.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Safety and Security:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;Safety is our top priority. We adhere to strict safety\r\nmeasures and use the state-of-the-art technology to ensure the well-being of\r\nour passengers. Our competent &amp; skilled staff works tirelessly to create a\r\nsafe environment throughout our metro network.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Employment and Skills Development:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;PMRCL prides itself on its role as a begetter of employment\r\nopportunities. By promoting skill development, we help to improve the\r\nemployability of local populace.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Technological Advancement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;We rely on technological innovations to improve the\r\nefficiency and effectiveness of our metro services. From advanced signaling\r\nsystems to user-friendly applications, we are committed to leveraging the\r\nlatest advancements for the benefit of our valued passengers.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Transparency and Accountability:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;PMRCL operates with the utmost transparency and\r\naccountability. We value the trust that our stakeholders place in us and ensure\r\nthat our decision-making processes are open, fair and in line with the best\r\npractices in corporate governance.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Together with the support of the\r\nGovernment, our dedicated team, and the people of Patna, we are committed to\r\nbuilding a world-class metro network that will not only serve the city\'s\r\ngrowing population, but also act as a catalyst for economic development and\r\nsocial progress.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Thank you for choosing&nbsp;<b>Patna\r\nMetro Rail Corporation Limited</b>&nbsp;as your preferred mode of\r\ntransportation. Let us embark together on a journey to a greener, better\r\nconnected and prosperous Patna.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">If you have any questions or\r\nsuggestions, please feel free to contact us. We are here to serve you better.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">The Team of Patna Metro Rail\r\nCorporation Limited<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:=\"\" major-bidi;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-bidi;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'About PMRCL', '2023-09-20 04:13:43', '2024-12-04 00:07:55'),
(5, NULL, 1, 3, 1, 1, 'Vision and Mission', 'vision-and-mission', 'Vision and Mission', 'Vision and Mission', 'Vision and Mission', '<p><strong>Our mission:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our primary mission is to build a state-of-the-art metro network in Patna that provides seamless connections, reduces traffic congestion, and promotes environmentally friendly commuting options. We strive to provide safe, reliable and affordable transportation solutions to the city&#39;s residents, commuters and visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Vision:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our vision at Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL) is to create a modern and sustainable metro rail network that revolutionizes urban transportation in Patna. Our goal is to create an integrated and efficient public transport system that connects key areas, promotes economic growth, and improves the overall quality of life for the people of Patna.</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, 0, 'Vision and Mission', '2023-09-20 04:20:01', '2025-01-24 00:22:14'),
(6, NULL, 1, 3, 1, 1, 'Vision  Mission', 'vision-mission', 'Vision  Mission', 'Vision  Mission', 'Vision  Mission', '<p><b>Our\r\nmission:\r\n</b></p><p>\r\nOur primary mission\r\nis to build a state-of-the-art metro network in Patna that provides seamless connectivity,\r\nreduces traffic congestion, and promotes environment friendly commuting\r\noptions. We strive to provide safe, reliable and affordable transportation\r\nsolutions to the city\'s residents, commuters and visitors.\r\n</p><p><b>\r\nOur\r\nVision:\r\n</b></p><p>\r\nOur vision at Patna\r\nMetro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL) is to create a modern and sustainable\r\nmetro rail network that revolutionizes urban transportation in Patna. Our goal\r\nis to create an integrated and efficient public transport system that connects\r\nkey areas, promotes economic growth, and improves the overall quality of life\r\nfor the people of Patna.</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'Vision amp Mission', '2023-09-20 04:28:17', '2023-10-23 03:30:52'),
(7, NULL, 1, 3, 1, 1, 'MD’s Message', 'mds-message', 'MD’s Message', 'MD’s Message', 'MD’s Message', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Dear Patrons and Stakeholders,</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you all to the official website of Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL). As the Managing Director of PMRCL, I am honored to lead a dynamic team dedicated to revolutionizing public transport in the city of Patna.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Our vision at PMRCL is to create a modern and sustainable metro network that will revolutionize urban transportation in Patna. Our goal is to create an integrated and efficient public transportation system that connects key areas, promotes economic growth, and improves the overall quality of life for the people of Patna. Our main goal is to build a state-of-the-art metro network in Patna that will provide seamless connections, reduce traffic congestion, and promote environment friendly commuting options. We aim to provide safe, reliable and affordable transportation solutions to the city\'s residents, commuters and visitors.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">As we embark on this remarkable journey, our commitment to our passengers remains unwavering. Our customer-centric approach aims to provide you with a safe, comfortable and reliable travel experience. From the moment you enter our metro stations to until you reach your destination, we want you to feel comfortable and know that you are in the hands of a service that truly cares.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Safety is at the heart of everything we do. We have stringent security measures in place to ensure that our Metro system meets the highest safety standards. Our focus on using cutting-edge technology and industry best practices ensures that you can place your trust in Patna Metro.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">PMRCL also recognizes its responsibility to environmental sustainability. In building and operating our metro network, we strive to minimize our environmental impact by incorporating environment friendly practices into our daily operations. By promoting public transportation and moving away from private transport, we hope to contribute to a greener and cleaner Patna.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">The success of our efforts depends not only on the commitment of our team, but also on the support and cooperation of the people of Patna. We greatly appreciate the trust you place in us and are committed to transparency and accountability in all our actions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">As we move forward, we continuously strive for innovation and excellence, focusing on technological advances that enhance our services and enrich your travel experience. We are committed to the spirit of progress while remaining true to our values of integrity, inclusivity and social responsibility.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">I invite you all to join Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited on this transformative journey. Together, let us build a city that evolves with confidence, sustainability and pride.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Thank you for choosing Patna Metro as your preferred mode of transportation. We look forward to having you on board.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Yours sincerely,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\">Sh. Abhay\r\nKumar Singh, IAS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">(Managing Director)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: \" century=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited&nbsp;</span></p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'MD’s Message', '2023-09-20 04:29:25', '2024-12-04 00:10:41'),
