(12, NULL, 1, 11, 1, 1, 'Why PMRCL', 'why-pmrcl', 'Why PMRCL', 'Why PMRCL', 'Why PMRCL', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Why PMRCL?</b></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Redesigning Urban Mobility:</b> Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL) aims to revolutionize the way people move around the city. With our state-of-the-art metro network, we provide a reliable, safe, efficient and affordable mode of transportation that significantly reduces travel time and traffic congestion.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>World-class infrastructure: </b>at PMRCL, we pride ourselves on our modern and well-designed metro stations, equipped with the latest technology. Our air-conditioned trains are spacious, comfortable and designed to accommodate a large number of passengers, ensuring a pleasant journey for all.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Customer-oriented approach:</b> your comfort and satisfaction are our top priority. Our well-trained personnel are always ready to provide the excellent customer service. Our user-friendly mobile app and ticketing systems make commuting by metro car a breeze.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Safety First: </b>Safety is at the heart of everything we do. PMRCL adheres to the highest safety standards, from the construction phase to the daily operation of the Metro network. Our commitment to your well-being is unwavering.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Environmentally Sustainable:</b> PMRCL recognizes the importance of sustainable transportation for a greener future. By promoting public transport, we aim to reduce carbon emissions and create a cleaner environment for Patna.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Supporting urban development: </b>with a vision for smart urban growth, PMRCL\'s metro network catalyzes development, improves connectivity to key areas of the city, and promotes economic growth.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Job creation and skills development: </b>As we expand our operations, PMRCL creates jobs for local residents and focuses on skills development, contributing to the overall growth of the region.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Transparency and accountability:</b> PMRCL operate in a transparent and accountable manner, keeping stakeholders informed of our progress, projects and initiatives.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Accessibility and inclusivity:</b> we strive to make our metro network accessible to all, so that people with disabilities and the elderly can comfortably use our services.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Part of Patna\'s heritage: </b>As the capital of Bihar, Patna has a rich cultural heritage. PMRCL is proud to be a part of this heritage as we work towards a more modern, connected and vibrant Patna.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">When you choose Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited, you are choosing a future where commuting is not only efficient and convenient, but also environment friendly. We invite you to join us on this transformative journey as we build a city that evolves with progress, sustainability and prosperity.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Welcome aboard the Patna Metro!</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us. We are here to serve you better.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font face=\"Century Gothic, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sincerely yours,</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nAptos;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">The Team of Patna\r\nMetro Rail Corporation Limited</span></b><br></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'Why PMRCL', '2023-09-20 04:34:19', '2024-08-20 04:49:17'),
