(30, NULL, 1, 21, 1, 1, 'Do’s  Don’ts', 'dos-donts', 'Do’s  Don’ts', 'Do’s  Don’ts', 'Do’s  Don’ts', '<div><b>Commandments and prohibitions for Patna Metro:</b></div><div>Welcome to Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL)!&nbsp;</div><div>To ensure a safe, comfortable and enjoyable journey for all passengers, we request you to please abide the following rules of conduct during your ride in Patna Metro:</div><div>Do\'s:</div><div>1.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Valid Tickets:</b> always make sure you have a valid ticket before entering the metro station and carry it with you throughout your ride.</div><div>2.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Line up and wait:</b> Form a line when waiting to board the metro car and let the passengers to get off before boarding.</div><div>3.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Keep the stations clean: </b>Help us to maintain the cleanliness by using the trash cans provided at the stations and not littering elsewhere.</div><div>4.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Priority Seating:</b> Please respect the priority seating of senior citizens, pregnant women and people with disabilities (Divyangs).</div><div>5.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Be Courteous: </b>Be respectful and considerate of fellow passengers and metro personnel.</div><div>6.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Hold onto handrails: </b>For your safety, hold onto handrails when standing or walking in metro cars.</div><div>7.<b><span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Keep emergency exits clear: </b>Do not block emergency exits or doors while boarding or exiting the train.</div><div>8.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Report suspicious activity: </b>If you notice any suspicious activity or unattended luggage, please inform the metro personnel immediately.</div><div>Prohibitions:</div><div>1.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No smoking:</b> Smoking is strictly prohibited at metro stations and trains.</div><div>2.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No Eating or Drinking:</b> Please do not eat or drink on metro premises.</div><div>3.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No defacing property: </b>Graffiti or defacing Metro property is not permitted and may result in penalties.</div><div>4.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No Trespassing:</b> Do not enter restricted areas or cross the tracks; use designated crosswalks.</div><div>5.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No unauthorized sales:</b> do not purchase tickets from unauthorized vendors; use authorized ticket counters or machines.</div><div>6.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No blocking doors: </b>do not block closing doors or attempt to force them open.</div><div>7.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No unauthorized photography: </b>Photography or filming for commercial purposes requires a permit.</div><div>8.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>No loud music:</b> keep the volume of your personal devices low to create a quiet environment.</div><div><br></div><div>By following these guidelines, you will contribute to a safe and enjoyable metro ride for yourself and others. Let us work together to build a responsible and respectful commuter community.</div><div>In the event of an emergency or if you need any assistance, please feel free to contact our metro personnel or use the emergency call boxes at the stations and on trains.</div><div>Thank you for your kind co-operation and for choosing the Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited as your preferred mode of transportation.</div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>The team of Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited</div><div><br></div>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'Do’s amp Don’ts', '2023-09-21 00:20:26', '2023-10-23 04:19:20'),
(31, NULL, 1, 21, 1, 1, 'PMRCL-Facilities for differently abled', 'pmrcl-facilities-for-differently-a', 'PMRCL-Facilities for differently abled', 'PMRCL-Facilities for differently a', 'PMRCL-Facilities for differently a', '<div><b>Barrier-free access for people with disabilities (Divyangs):</b></div><div>At Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL), we are committed to create an inclusive and accessible environment for all passengers, including people with disabilities (Divyangs). We believe that every person should have the opportunity to travel with dignity and independence. To ensure an accessible experience, we have created a range of facilities and services tailored to the needs of people with disabilities (Divyangs).</div><div>1.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Accessible stations:</b> all metro stations are equipped with ramps, elevators, and tactile paving that allow easy access for wheelchair users and people with mobility impairments.</div><div>2.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Preferential boarding:</b> We give priority boarding and alighting to people with disabilities (Divyangs), ensuring a seamless and comfortable transition onto the metro cars.</div><div>3.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Reserved seating: </b>There are seats reserved for passengers with disabilities (Divyangs) in the metro cars to ensure their comfort during the journey.</div><div>4.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Staff assistance: </b>Our station staffs are trained to assist passengers with disabilities (Divyangs) and to accompany them to the platforms and answer their queries.</div><div>5.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Visual and audio announcements: </b>All stations and Metro cars are equipped with visual and audio announcement system so that the travel information is accessible to the people with visual or hearing impairments.</div><div>6.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Accessible ticket counters: </b>Ticket counters at metro stations are designed to access the people with disabilities (Divyangs), with adequate height.</div><div>7.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Emergency assistance: </b>In emergency situation, there are intercoms present in every metro car and at every station that connect the passengers directly to our staff for immediate assistance.</div><div>8.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Signage in Braille:</b> To assist passengers with visual impairments, signs in Braille are posted at key locations such as elevators, ticket counters and in metro cars.</div><div>9.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Accessible restrooms:</b> Accessible restrooms are available at every metro stations.</div><div><br></div><div>We are committed to improve and expand our accessibility initiatives to ensure an inclusive and empowering travel experience for all. Feedback from passengers is invaluable to us in making improvements and addressing specific needs.</div><div>If you need any assistance during the trip or having suggestions to improve the accessibility, please feel free to contact our customer service team. Your comfort and convenience are our top and foremost priority.</div><div>Thank you for choosing Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited. Let us work together to create an accessible and inclusive transportation system for all.</div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>The team of Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited</div><div><br></div>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'PMRCL-Facilities for differently a', '2023-09-21 00:21:00', '2023-11-28 01:52:20'),
(32, NULL, 1, 21, 1, 1, 'Facilities for Women', 'facilities-for-women', 'Facilities for Women', 'Facilities for Women', 'Facilities for Women', '<div><b>Facilities for women passengers:</b></div><div>At Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited (PMRCL), the safety, comfort and well-being of our women passengers are of paramount importance. We are committed to providing a safe and inclusive environment for all commuters and have introduced various facilities and measures specifically designed to cater to the needs of women passengers.</div><div>1.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b style=\"\">Women-only Coaches:</b> Special women\'s coaches are available on all metro trains at certain times to ensure a safe and comfortable journey for female passengers. These coaches are clearly marked and open to women of all ages.</div><div>2.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>CCTV surveillance:</b> we have installed an extensive network of CCTV cameras at all metro stations and on trains to enhance security and monitor passenger activity.</div><div>3.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Emergency intercoms: </b>emergency intercoms are installed in every metro car and at stations, allowing direct communication with metro personnel if an emergency occurs or any assistance is needed.</div><div>4.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Station Staff Assistance: </b>Our well-trained and courteous station staff is available to assist female passengers with any questions or assistance they may need during their metro ride.</div><div>5.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Accessible restrooms:</b> Women\'s restrooms are available at all metro stations, providing clean and hygienic facilities for female commuters.</div><div>6.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Security Personnel:</b> Trained security personnel are stationed at all metro stations to ensure a safe environment for all passengers, with special attention to the needs of female travelers.</div><div>7.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Reserved Parking: </b>At select Metro stations, we offer designated parking spaces for female passengers, ensuring convenient and easy access.</div><div>8.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Security Escort Service:</b> In cooperation with local law enforcement, we provide security escort services upon request, especially late at night to ensure the safety of women traveling alone.</div><div>9.<span style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span><b>Accessibility:</b> we strive to provide accessible facilities for women with disabilities or special needs to enable them to travel comfortably and hassle-free.</div><div>PMRCL is constantly striving to improve our services and facilities to meet the diverse needs of all our passengers. We encourage female passengers to take advantage of these facilities and travel with confidence in Patna Metro.</div><div>We welcome your feedback and suggestions to improve the overall experience for female passengers. Please feel free to contact our dedicated customer care team if you have any questions or need assistance.</div><div>Thank you for choosing Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited. Let us work together to create a safe and encouraging commuter experience for women in Patna.</div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>The Team of Patna Metro Rail Corporation Limited</div><div><br></div>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'Facilities for Women', '2023-09-21 00:21:35', '2023-10-23 04:13:01'),
