(72, NULL, 1, 0, 3, 1, 'RTI', 'rti', 'RTI', 'RTI', 'RTI', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;color:#333333;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">How to\r\nfile an RTI Application<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">A citizen of India who desires to obtain an\r\ninformation under the Right to Information Act, 2005 (Act) may make a request\r\nby sending an application to the Public Information Officer, Patna Metro Rail Corporation\r\nLimited, 7<sup>th</sup> Floor, Indira Bhawan, Boring Canal Road, Patna, &nbsp;PIN - 800015.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Application Fee<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">An application for obtaining information under the\r\nRTI Act shall be accompanied by a fee of Rs.10/-.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Mode of Payment<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Fee can be paid by postal order or court fee stamp\r\nor by demand draft or banker cheque drawn in favour of Patna Metro Rail Corporation\r\nLimited.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Persons who belong to BPL (below poverty line) are\r\nnot required to pay any fee, provided copy of the certificate issued by the\r\nappropriate Government in this regard is submitted along with the application.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Additional Fee</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">In case additional fees are required for providing\r\ninformation, the applicant will be informed about the same.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Such additional fee for providing information shall\r\nbe charged at the rates as specified in the Right to Information Rules, 2012.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'RTI', '2023-09-21 01:24:21', '2023-12-02 03:47:24'),
